      <title>为什么托管式安全信息与事件管理(SIEM)是现代网络防御的基石</title>
      <link>https://qife122.github.io/p/%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%89%98%E7%AE%A1%E5%BC%8F%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86siem%E6%98%AF%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E9%98%B2%E5%BE%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%9F%B3/</link>
